Successful conference - people were engaged, unusually great # of people discussing free culture issues - most attendance since 2011.  Important to have our own 
Free Culture Conference to revel in free culture.  People were engaged & learned how to apply free culture principles for advocacy.  Got next steps started.

    Turnout 2nd day was lower.


